flowchart LR
    ISSUE["Issue (Sonnet)"]
    PLAN["Plan (Opus)"]
    CRITIQUE{"Critique (Opus)"}
    BUILD["Build (Sonnet)"]
    TEST{"Test (Sonnet)"}
    PATCH["Patch (Sonnet)"]
    REVIEW{"Review (Opus)"}
    DOCS["Docs (Sonnet)"]
    MERGE((Merge))

    ISSUE --> PLAN
    PLAN --> CRITIQUE
    CRITIQUE -->|ready| BUILD
    CRITIQUE -->|concerns| PLAN
    BUILD --> TEST
    TEST -->|pass| REVIEW
    TEST -->|fail| PATCH
    PATCH --> TEST
    REVIEW -->|approved| DOCS
    REVIEW -->|findings| PATCH
    DOCS --> MERGE

    PATCH -.->|hard patch: resume builder| BUILD
